movie_name: Une collection d'art et de sang, le catalogue Goering
short_description: Over more than a decade, Hermann Göring amassed over 5,000 works of art meticulously in a catalog. But what drove Nazi Germany's second most powerful man to loot art from Jewish families who fell victim to the Holocaust?
